Description: Provides tools to parse, collapse, and deidentify WebVTT transcript files.
    The package supports batch processing of transcripts, speaker relabeling,
    name redaction, and export to formatted Word documents. Designed for use
    in research workflows that require structured and reproducible transcript
    deidentification.
